          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/7ce5c658d0c908bd65c8389962816b7c_2471552691358025468.png",
                "id": "talent22133",
                "key": "Dawnstar Piercer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dawnstar Piercer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Icy Quill</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Icy Quill</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span></p><p>Your character deals 1 increased <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> (Includes the DMG triggered by <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo-infused</span> Swirl reactions)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/5d89f864c57233f72005e0f35858ff63_1958439209077284127.png",
                "id": "talent66910",
                "key": "Spring Spirit Summoning",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Spring Spirit Summoning"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Talisman Spirit</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/e6afe89821ff613100ed8fd264f93dda_5020957099746542040.png",
                "id": "talent19347",
                "key": "Divine Maiden's Deliverance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Divine Maiden's Deliverance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When this Summon is on the field</span>: Opposing character(s) take +1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5601380149171856663.png",
                "id": "talent76201",
                "key": "Talisman Spirit",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/48fc5942249b75b9a938f06c0f87edf3_9183571496244191363.gif",
                "title": "Talisman Spirit"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_8558713363155512826.png",
                "id": "talent55668",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1815848705703729077.png",
